    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your connection to eldritch domains has uncovered a relic for you: a talisman. This talisman resizes to comfortably fit around the wearer's neck. While wearing this talisman, you gain the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Bolstered Abilities.</strong> When the wearer fails an ability check, they can add a d4 to the roll, potentially turning the roll into a success. This benefit can be used a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus and all expended uses are restored when you finish a Long Rest.</p><p><strong>Psychic Retaliation.</strong> When the wearer of your talisman takes damage from a creature you can see within 30 feet of you, you can take a Reaction to deal Psychic damage to the creature equal to your Proficiency Bonus and push it up to 10 feet away from the talisman's wearer.</p><p>If the talisman is lost or destroyed, you can perform a 1-hour ceremony to uncover a replacement. This ceremony can be performed during a Short or Long Rest, and it destroys the previous talisman. The talisman turns to mundane ash when you die.</p>",
